642
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:22,530
Mo Fei, your old tea-horse road designs are the best-selling items in Fashion Daily!

643
00:40:22,530 --> 00:40:24,890
- For real?
- Yes, look!

644
00:40:24,890 --> 00:40:26,240
You can keep chatting, I will go to work.

645
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:28,060
Don't walk away, Jiaxi!

646
00:40:28,060 --> 00:40:31,270
