655
00:40:59,770 --> 00:41:01,530
Zheng Hang, are you not trying your best,

656
00:41:01,530 --> 00:41:04,370
or does Haiyao really not have any talented designers?

657
00:41:04,370 --> 00:41:08,060
Director Bai, don't get angry! It's been a while!

658
00:41:08,060 --> 00:41:11,680
You also know the situation of our company's designers.

659
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:14,070
